{"id": 1404, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都看腻了哪些老套的动漫梗？", "description": "现如今，看到主角死了我的内心毫无波动甚至还想笑，因为我知道不出一集TA又会活过来！（题图来自：xoana herrera）", "record_count": 5527, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201612221503164txTIowYWAS5vgZO.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-12-24T17:00:29Z", "options": [{"id": 157441, "content": "发大招之前总是有说不完的话和慢镜头。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913692}, {"id": 163329, "content": "主角身世凄惨", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922043}, {"id": 147202, "content": "主角光环", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700908}, {"id": 147458, "content": "嘴炮", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 880145}, {"id": 148482, "content": "不管主角开始的时候是不是弱到令人发指的地步，最后总会遇见命中的贵人，然后开启开挂的人生", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 883501}, {"id": 149250, "content": "男主或女主一开始什么都不知道，因为主角特有的能力什么的被美女或帅哥强行带到一个本来完全没接触过的世界。然后就一直升级，被人爱吧啦吧啦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 878454}, {"id": 160514, "content": "三角恋上的恩爱情仇", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896039}, {"id": 147203, "content": "主角的嘴炮技能没有CD时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879296}, {"id": 147459, "content": "你以为这个boss已经很腻害了？不好意思还有更厉害的。你以为这个想要称霸地球的已经是强，无敌了，马上你又会看到可以毁灭全宇宙的。总之，没有最强，只有更强。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 880151}, {"id": 147204, "content": "回忆", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 3365}, {"id": 147460, "content": "超级赛亚人……嗷的一声，头发又长了……嗷的一声蓝了拥有神力了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 240990}, {"id": 149508, "content": "开始被完虐然后开始回忆过去然后亢奋的要日天  某影忍者", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 885910}, {"id": 163076, "content": "好人的装备似乎总比坏人差", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927285}, {"id": 147461, "content": "主角永远是前期太废，后期能一打一群的漫画", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 880155}, {"id": 156421, "content": "热血漫主角都有个牛逼的老爸～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 875168}, {"id": 147206, "content": "走哪儿哪儿死人的死神光环，对我说的就是你柯南", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 422542}, {"id": 147207, "content": "奏凯   这是我的对手！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879492}, {"id": 147463, "content": "卢克 ·天行者被西迪厄斯电疗时，爵爷突然倒戈……你们看星战吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634415}, {"id": 147208, "content": "被反派打趴下然后小宇宙爆发再把反派打趴下", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163303}, {"id": 147464, "content": "男主永远有后宫", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 875954}, {"id": 151816, "content": "嘴炮", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896785}, {"id": 147209, "content": "配角活不长", "image": "img/option/option/20161225090421McqAo7pEeKIWC6Qn", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 878363}, {"id": 148489, "content": "回忆杀", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 404667}, {"id": 149257, "content": "回忆杀", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 885132}, {"id": 155657, "content": "boss开大死不了，自己爆个气boss就残血了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891973}, {"id": 147210, "content": "主角总是被敌人虐了千百次以后才爆发出潜能打败对手，主角说单挑就是真的单挑，队友一炮能打死的事，非不去帮忙w", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879502}, {"id": 147466, "content": "反派的话太多", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 874609}, {"id": 147211, "content": "故事情节单子 总是一个事儿 好人战胜坏人 就该结束了～", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 718332}, {"id": 147467, "content": "男主和女主必先打一架才能最后在一起", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713394}, {"id": 147212, "content": "男主去洗澡女主必随后到", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 735966}, {"id": 148492, "content": "意淫", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855827}, {"id": 151820, "content": "就差最后一招打死主角，boos是要瞎bibi", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896806}, {"id": 147213, "content": "女主上课迟到叼面包，拐角撞到就是男主", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 735966}, {"id": 150029, "content": "反派死于话多", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 876023}, {"id": 165133, "content": "嘴炮，眼泪", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 932273}, {"id": 147214, "content": "反派死于话多", "image": null, "praise_count": 288, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879518}, {"id": 147470, "content": "反派比主角励志多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162377}, {"id": 147982, "content": "如果该动漫有重要配角死亡，总是会有无间断的回忆，煽情，尤其是！打boss的时候！然后主角痛哭流涕，秒了大boss", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 774860}, {"id": 147215, "content": "你们让那些不用打怪的吐槽漫说什么才好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 850681}, {"id": 147471, "content": "大家，是伙伴的力量！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 880207}, {"id": 151823, "content": "Boos只有一条命，主角永远打不死", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896806}, {"id": 147217, "content": "男二(男主的朋友)不死则残。举个例子，美队和巴基◀▶", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 870050}, {"id": 147985, "content": "从一开始就告诉所有人，自己的梦想，然后朝着前进，遇上了什么困难，解不出来 然后出去一趟，发生什么事就豁然开朗了……那都不是事", "image": "img/option/option/20161227075557t71RydJ20NfkKDjX", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 359974}, {"id": 151313, "content": "找宝贝，打老怪。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893792}, {"id": 151825, "content": "就跟唐僧肉一样，每次抓了都不吃，一定得等到猴子来救", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737816}, {"id": 150290, "content": "BGM突然响起！男主内心旁白：现在移开目光的话，我会后悔的⋯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 889273}, {"id": 153874, "content": "决斗的时候，总有那么多的话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 904822}, {"id": 147219, "content": "女主因为一些小事莫名其妙的爱上男猪脚", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852809}, {"id": 147220, "content": "为什么都没有床戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149193}, {"id": 147221, "content": "不符合重力定律的女主的短裙", "image": null, "praise_count": 73, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836711}]}